name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`BRANCH`,
t1.`BUGS`,
t1.`BUILDER`,
t1.`DATE`,
t1.`DELETED`,
t1.`DESC`,
t1.`FILEPATH`,
t1.`ID`,
CONCAT_WS('','PMS ',t1.`name`,' 主要更新') as `NAME`,
t1.`PRODUCT`,
t11.`NAME` AS `PRODUCTNAME`,
t1.`PROJECT`,
t1.`SCMPATH`,
t1.`STORIES`,
t1.BUILDSN
FROM `zt_build` t1 
LEFT JOIN zt_product t11 ON t1.PRODUCT = t11.productsn
